18 declamatio: ³ Bombastic delivery.' Cf. l. 21 ingentibus verbis. With the thought, cp. Quint. II 12, 9 IV 2, 37. 39 XI 3,184. On the ordinary meaning of the word, cf. 0. 31 2.—-tyrannicidarum praemia: The great popularity of these particular themes was doubtless due to the fact, that they affor-ded the only opportunity in an age of despotism for the expression of anti-monarchical sentiments, under the seemingly innocent guise of school exercises, although some emperors occasionally resorted to harsh measures in suppressing even these.
